Package: zFactor
Type: Package
Title: Calculate the compressibility factor, Z, for hydrocarbons
Version: 0.0.0.9011
Author: Alfonso R. Reyes <alfonso.reyes@oilgainsanalytics.com>
Maintainer: Alfonso R. Reyes <alfonso.reyes@oilgainsanalytics.com>
Description: Computational algorithms to solve equations and find the
    compresibility factor (z). Equations available: Hall-Yarborough, 
    Dranchuk-AbuKassem and Dranchuk-Purvis-Robinson.
Imports: rootSolve, tidyr, ggplot2
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown, testthat
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)    
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
